    "These can contain many claims, whose factuality need not be consistent with each other 3.",
    "Publisher: experts label publishers for their propensity for factual reporting, based on historical records and prescribed authorial intent.",
    "These labels are often used as a proxy for finer-grained labels.",
    "The articles produced by publishers do not necessarily have the same label as the publisher",
